hingga makan tahu pagi-pagi
di depan kantor polisi?

226
00:17:18,538 --> 00:17:20,999
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Jika petroleum mendadak menghilang,</font></i>

227
00:17:21,082 --> 00:17:22,751
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">dunia akan seperti apa?</font></i>

228
00:17:22,834 --> 00:17:25,920
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Kebanyakan mobil, pesawat, dan kereta</font></i>

229
00:17:26,004 --> 00:17:27,547
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">akan berhenti berjalan.</font></i>

230
00:17:27,630 --> 00:17:29,382
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Toko-toko akan kosong,</font></i>

231
00:17:29,466 --> 00:17:32,010
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">karena tak ada barang yang bisa dibeli.</font></i>

232
00:17:32,093 --> 00:17:37,390
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Sebagian besar mesin yang membuat pulpen,</font></i>
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">tas, piring, dan peralatan</font></i>

233
00:17:37,474 --> 00:17:39,684
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">bergantung pada petroleum.</font></i>

234
00:17:39,768 --> 00:17:43,855
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Faktanya, bahan bakar fosil amat terbatas.</font></i>

235
00:17:43,938 --> 00:17:46,191
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Kita tak tahu kapan akan habis.</font></i>

236
00:17:46,274 --> 00:17:48,193
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Tak perlu mencoba mengingatnya.</font></i>

237
00:17:48,777 --> 00:17:51,237
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Pertemuanku dengan dia tak mungkin baik.</font></i>

238
00:17:52,197 --> 00:17:55,116
{\an8}<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Kita telah belajar</font></i>
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">energi berkelanjutan dan ramah lingkungan,</font></i>

239
00:17:55,200 --> 00:17:56,951
{\an8}<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">serta energi baru terbarukan.</font></i>

240
00:17:57,035 --> 00:17:58,328
KLUB LINGKUNGAN
GREEN NARAE

241
00:17:59,704 --> 00:18:03,458
Kita sudah membahas
jenis-jenis energi dan fungsinya.

242
00:18:03,541 --> 00:18:04,417
Bu.

243
00:18:05,168 --> 00:18:07,504
Kita akan selalu di kelas?

244
00:18:08,087 --> 00:18:10,548
Kudengar klub drone belajar di lapangan.

245
00:18:11,633 --> 00:18:13,092
Di lapangan, apanya?

246
00:18:13,176 --> 00:18:15,386
Kenapa? Kau tak suka ke lapangan?

247
00:18:16,262 --> 00:18:17,514
Bukan begitu.

248
00:18:18,556 --> 00:18:20,141
Dia guru pertukaran.

249
00:18:20,225 --> 00:18:23,061
Kurasa dia tak mau susah payah untuk klub.

250
00:18:23,978 --> 00:18:24,896
Guru pertukaran?

251
00:18:25,522 --> 00:18:27,649
Kalau begitu, Ibu akan kembali ke Seoul?

252
00:18:27,732 --> 00:18:28,858
Kapan?

253
00:18:30,360 --> 00:18:33,822
Kapan pun itu, selagi di sini,
aku adalah pembimbing klub

254
00:18:33,905 --> 00:18:36,616
dan akan berusaha sebisaku
untuk membimbing, jadi…

255
00:18:36,699 --> 00:18:37,534
Bu.

256
00:18:38,827 --> 00:18:41,955
Aku tahu satu pembangkit listrik.
Bisa kita ke sana?

257
00:18:42,789 --> 00:18:44,582
Kau tahu pembangkit listrik?

258
00:18:45,166 --> 00:18:47,043
Pamanku kerja di pembangkit listrik.

259
00:18:49,504 --> 00:18:51,464
Pamanmu punya pekerjaan?

260
00:18:57,971 --> 00:18:59,722
Ya, dia punya pekerjaan.

261
00:19:02,392 --> 00:19:05,436
Maksudku, dia berkeliaran di siang hari

262
00:19:05,520 --> 00:19:07,146
dan bersama pria-pria seram.

263
00:19:07,230 --> 00:19:09,107
Aku melihatnya di kantor polisi.

264
00:19:09,190 --> 00:19:11,568
Kukira dia suka satai ayam pedas,

265
00:19:11,651 --> 00:19:13,027
tetapi dia juga suka tahu.

266
00:19:14,821 --> 00:19:16,281
Pembangkit listrik mana?

267
00:19:16,865 --> 00:19:18,449
Yang tampak di jalur Bus 23.

268
00:19:19,367 --> 00:19:21,786
Yang ada kincir angin
dan cantik saat sore?

269
00:19:21,870 --> 00:19:22,996
Kita ke sana saja.

270
00:19:23,079 --> 00:19:24,664
Aku juga mau pergi ke sana.

271
00:19:27,959 --> 00:19:29,377
Itu… Tidak.

272
00:19:29,460 --> 00:19:31,671
Nanti kucari pembangkit listrik lain.

273
00:19:32,463 --> 00:19:34,340
Jadi, "energi baru terbarukan"

274
00:19:35,508 --> 00:19:39,095
adalah kombinasi kata "energi baru"
dan "energi terbarukan".

275
00:19:39,679 --> 00:19:43,391
Kalian tahu bahan bakar fosil
menyebabkan kerusakan lingkungan, kan?

276
00:19:44,017 --> 00:19:48,062
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Untuk mencegahnya,</font></i>
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">bahan bakar fosil yang ada digunakan ulang</font></i>

277
00:19:48,146 --> 00:19:50,148
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">atau diubah menjadi energi terbarukan</font></i>

278
00:19:50,231 --> 00:19:52,525
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">untuk membuatnya ramah lingkungan.</font></i>

279
00:19:52,609 --> 00:19:56,154
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Ada berbagai jenis seperti tenaga surya,</font></i>
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">angin, dan biomassa.</font></i>

280
00:20:01,868 --> 00:20:04,120
Hei, jangan dorong. Astaga.

281
00:20:04,203 --> 00:20:05,163
Bisa lebih cepat?

282
00:20:39,656 --> 00:20:40,740
Oper.

283
00:20:45,828 --> 00:20:48,831
Astaga, kapan selesainya? Minggir.

284
00:20:48,915 --> 00:20:51,167
Tidak, tunggu. Berhenti.

285
00:20:51,250 --> 00:20:52,085
Bos.

286
00:20:52,669 --> 00:20:56,965
Haruskah kujelaskan penyebab
Revolusi Petani Donghak?

287
00:20:58,216 --> 00:21:01,803
Meski kau tak merokok,
anggap saja ini istirahat merokok.

288
00:21:02,971 --> 00:21:03,888
Baiklah.

289
00:21:04,889 --> 00:21:06,432
Aku duduk saja, ya?

290
00:21:14,857 --> 00:21:15,775
Ya, halo?

291
00:21:15,858 --> 00:21:17,986
Sabuk Hitam, ini Putih.

292
00:21:18,069 --> 00:21:19,862
Kau bisa bicara?

293
00:21:22,281 --> 00:21:23,116
Apa?

294
00:21:26,327 --> 00:21:27,328
Aku mengerti.

295
00:21:27,912 --> 00:21:30,206
Urus tanpa aku. Aku kembali nanti.

296
00:21:31,082 --> 00:21:31,916
Apa?

297
00:21:41,551 --> 00:21:42,427
Astaga.

298
00:21:43,928 --> 00:21:46,556
Kau melarang Green Narae
mengunjungi tempat kerjaku?

299
00:21:47,223 --> 00:21:48,850
Kau punya CCTV di sekolah?

300
00:21:48,933 --> 00:21:51,644
Bagaimana kau tahu
kejadian 145 menit lalu?

301
00:21:52,186 --> 00:21:54,689
Beri alasan logis
kenapa perusahaanku tidak dipilih.

302
00:21:55,273 --> 00:21:56,733
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Aku tak boleh terjebak.</font></i>

303
00:21:56,816 --> 00:21:59,360
Guru boleh menentukan tempat.
Sampai jumpa.

304
00:21:59,444 --> 00:22:01,446
Jika bukan perusahaanku,

305
00:22:01,529 --> 00:22:04,282
Palryongpo Suho Energy berjarak 27 km,

306
00:22:04,365 --> 00:22:06,868
dan Seomigot Doseong Solar 35 km jauhnya.

307
00:22:06,951 --> 00:22:08,953
Sekolah juga tak punya mobil.

308
00:22:09,037 --> 00:22:11,247
Bagaimana anak-anak akan ke sana?

309
00:22:12,832 --> 00:22:16,627
Tak ada juga alasan logis
untuk kami memilih perusahanmu.

310
00:22:17,128 --> 00:22:18,004
Ada.

311
00:22:18,588 --> 00:22:19,422
Apa?

312
00:22:20,465 --> 00:22:23,384
Mereka menolak memberikan Bakti Orang Tua
kepada Han-gyul.

313
00:22:23,968 --> 00:22:25,053
Aku orang tuanya.

314
00:22:25,136 --> 00:22:27,638
Aku ingin teman-teman Han-gyul

315
00:22:27,722 --> 00:22:29,599
melihat pekerjaan pamannya.

316
00:22:29,682 --> 00:22:32,351
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Aku tak boleh terjebak, tetapi…</font></i>

317
00:22:37,190 --> 00:22:38,524
Akan kupertimbangkan.

318
00:22:39,150 --> 00:22:41,277
Jika kau tak yakin akan perusahaanku…

319
00:22:42,820 --> 00:22:44,530
kita bisa lihat di akhir pekan.

320
00:22:44,614 --> 00:22:47,075
-Kita berdua saja?
-Kau mau begitu?

321
00:22:47,158 --> 00:22:48,576
Tentu tidak.

322
00:22:48,659 --> 00:22:51,954
Ada Han-gyul, kenapa berdua?
Kita bisa pergi bertiga.

323
00:22:53,247 --> 00:22:54,332
Kau sudah setuju.

324
00:22:54,916 --> 00:22:56,626
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Apa? Aku terjebak.</font></i>

325
00:22:56,709 --> 00:22:59,420
Sabtu ini, pukul 12.00. Kujemput di rumah.

326
00:23:10,681 --> 00:23:11,974
Sial.

327
00:23:18,981 --> 00:23:20,858
RAPOR

328
00:23:21,484 --> 00:23:24,779
Bahasa Korea, posisi kedua.
Keseluruhan, posisi kedua.

329
00:23:24,862 --> 00:23:25,988
Peringkat dua.

330
00:23:26,489 --> 00:23:28,950
Semuanya dua!

331
00:23:32,620 --> 00:23:34,330
Kau ingat perkataanmu?

332
00:23:34,914 --> 00:23:37,458
Kau janji menjadi siswa terbaik
di SMA Shinsu.

333
00:23:37,542 --> 00:23:39,752
Kau janji akan peringkat satu.

334
00:23:39,836 --> 00:23:40,753
Aku?

335
00:23:40,837 --> 00:23:43,631
Aku tak berkata begitu. Itu keinginan Ibu.

336
00:23:43,714 --> 00:23:44,841
Seharusnya begitu.

337
00:23:44,924 --> 00:23:48,678
Kau tak tahu kita terjebak di pedesaan ini
agar kau peringkat satu?

338
00:23:50,138 --> 00:23:51,222
Kau harus ingat.

339
00:23:51,305 --> 00:23:54,475
Kau perlu terus mendapat
peringkat satu hingga lulus

340
00:23:54,559 --> 00:23:56,644
agar bisa menjadi orang kelas satu.

341
00:23:58,396 --> 00:23:59,730
Apa aku sapi?

342
00:23:59,814 --> 00:24:02,108
Kalian selalu membahas kelas satu.

343
00:24:02,191 --> 00:24:04,610
Jika kau mau sapi kelas satu,

344
00:24:04,694 --> 00:24:06,696
harga termurah adalah 99.000 won.

345
00:24:09,240 --> 00:24:11,909
Aku tak makan, karena kelasnya di atasku.

346
00:24:11,993 --> 00:24:12,827
Astaga.

347
00:24:13,369 --> 00:24:16,539
Bocah itu.
Andai kau belajar sekeras mulutmu.

348
00:24:16,622 --> 00:24:18,457
-Dasar kau…
-Astaga.

349
00:24:26,382 --> 00:24:29,760
Sial. Menyebalkan!

350
00:24:29,844 --> 00:24:31,387
Aku benci mereka!

351
00:24:35,808 --> 00:24:37,393
{\an8}JJUN

352
00:24:37,977 --> 00:24:39,020
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Di mana kau?</font></i>

353
00:24:40,980 --> 00:24:42,523
{\an8}<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Apa rencanamu akhir pekan ini?</font></i>

354
00:24:43,441 --> 00:24:45,443
{\an8}<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Boleh aku menginap di tempatmu?</font></i>

355
00:24:53,409 --> 00:24:55,328
Han-gyul, aku pulang.

356
00:24:56,120 --> 00:24:56,996
Hei.

357
00:24:58,831 --> 00:24:59,665
Ini.

358
00:25:01,834 --> 00:25:03,294
Panas.

359
00:25:04,212 --> 00:25:06,797
Katanya Dong-pyo telepon Paman lagi.

360
00:25:06,881 --> 00:25:07,924
Apa katanya?

361
00:25:08,507 --> 00:25:10,968
Paman menemui guruku dan berkelahi lagi?

362
00:25:11,052 --> 00:25:12,762
Berkelahi apanya?

363
00:25:12,845 --> 00:25:15,097
Kami berkompromi.

364
00:25:16,057 --> 00:25:19,185
Dia setuju memutuskan
setelah melihat tempatnya.

365
00:25:19,268 --> 00:25:20,353
Sungguh?

366
00:25:20,436 --> 00:25:21,312
Tentu saja.

367
00:25:21,896 --> 00:25:23,272
Kau tak kenal pamanmu?

368
00:25:24,774 --> 00:25:28,319
Kata anak-anak, dia tak mau pusing
karena dia guru pertukaran.

369
00:25:29,403 --> 00:25:31,447
Guru pertukaran? Apa itu?

370
00:25:31,530 --> 00:25:33,241
Dia akan ke Seoul lagi.

371
00:25:33,324 --> 00:25:34,158
Kenapa?

372
00:25:34,825 --> 00:25:36,494
-Kapan? Kenapa?
-Aku tak tahu.

373
00:25:37,912 --> 00:25:40,748
Namun, aku penasaran kenapa dia kemari.

374
00:25:42,124 --> 00:25:44,543
Kurasa semua teman
dan keluarganya ada di Seoul.

375
00:26:08,359 --> 00:26:09,193
Sun Jae-gyu.

376
00:26:11,362 --> 00:26:13,406
{\an8}Jika aku terjebak lagi hari ini,

377
00:26:13,489 --> 00:26:15,283
aku bukan manusia, tetapi cumi-cumi.

378
00:26:15,366 --> 00:26:17,159
Aku lobak kering.

379
00:26:22,039 --> 00:26:25,209
Baiklah. Hari yang suram dimulai lagi.

380
00:26:26,460 --> 00:26:27,503
Jangan tersenyum.

381
00:26:28,212 --> 00:26:29,463
Jangan senang.

382
00:26:30,339 --> 00:26:31,966
Jangan bahagia.

383
00:26:34,010 --> 00:26:35,011
Semangat.

384
00:26:35,094 --> 00:26:36,721
Sembilan puluh enam.

385
00:26:36,804 --> 00:26:38,306
Sembilan puluh tujuh.

386
00:26:38,389 --> 00:26:39,807
Sembilan puluh delapan.

387
00:26:40,433 --> 00:26:42,059
Sembilan puluh sembilan.

388
00:26:45,062 --> 00:26:47,481
Cuacanya sangat cerah hari ini.

389
00:26:47,565 --> 00:26:48,441
Cuaca mantap!

390
00:26:49,150 --> 00:26:50,192
Di mana Han-gyul?

391
00:26:51,902 --> 00:26:52,778
Halo, Bu Yoon.

392
00:26:53,863 --> 00:26:55,156
Aku duduk di belakang…

393
00:26:56,365 --> 00:26:57,700
Masuklah.

394
00:27:05,916 --> 00:27:07,710
Kenakan sabuk pengaman.

395
00:27:18,387 --> 00:27:19,680
Mari berangkat.

396
00:27:35,321 --> 00:27:36,697
Ada janji lain setelah ini?

397
00:27:37,948 --> 00:27:38,783
Tidak.

398
00:27:39,992 --> 00:27:41,827
Kukira kau mau ke pemakaman.

399
00:27:43,454 --> 00:27:46,707
Kau selalu pakai baju gelap,
seperti sedang berkabung.

400
00:27:49,877 --> 00:27:53,172
Kau baru saja mengkritik pakaianku?

401
00:27:53,255 --> 00:27:55,966
Lalu kau? Kenapa selalu berpakaian begitu?

402
00:27:56,050 --> 00:27:59,095
Pernahkah berpikir untuk
memperhatikan mode, bukan hanya fungsi?

403
00:28:01,055 --> 00:28:03,808
Pakaian kerja hanya harus nyaman.

404
00:28:04,308 --> 00:28:07,061
Lihat. Ini kain spandeks
elastis empat arah.

405
00:28:07,812 --> 00:28:09,980
Sangat nyaman untuk bekerja.

406
00:28:10,564 --> 00:28:12,149
Apa namamu "Bayangan"?

407
00:28:12,233 --> 00:28:14,151
SE-JIN

408
00:28:17,321 --> 00:28:18,239
Ya?

409
00:28:18,864 --> 00:28:21,659
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Kau suruh bicara langsung</font></i>
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">jika ada masalah.</font></i>

410
00:28:23,577 --> 00:28:24,495
Di mana?

411
00:28:27,039 --> 00:28:28,082
Aku mengerti.

412
00:28:29,959 --> 00:28:31,419
Paman, turunkan aku.

413
00:28:40,344 --> 00:28:43,597
Maaf, ada hal mendadak.
Aku menyusul nanti.

414
00:28:43,681 --> 00:28:44,557
Sampai nanti.

415
00:28:45,850 --> 00:28:47,309
Han-gyul!

416
00:28:49,228 --> 00:28:50,354
Ada apa denganmu?

417
00:28:50,438 --> 00:28:52,898
Kau biarkan dia pergi tanpa tanya kenapa?

418
00:28:52,982 --> 00:28:55,276
Dia bisa menjaga diri. Untuk apa cemas?

419
00:28:55,985 --> 00:28:57,236
Tetap saja…

420
00:28:58,070 --> 00:28:59,905
Jadi, bagaimana? Kita pergi tanpa dia?

421
00:29:00,614 --> 00:29:02,700
Kita harus pergi dengan dia.

422
00:29:03,617 --> 00:29:04,827
Berarti kita tunggu.

423
00:29:07,872 --> 00:29:09,039
Mau ke bioskop?

424
00:29:09,623 --> 00:29:11,584
Ke bioskop dengan orang tua siswa?

425
00:29:12,418 --> 00:29:13,711
Kalau begitu…

426
00:29:13,794 --> 00:29:16,630
Ada jalan setapak terpencil
di atas terowongan.

427
00:29:16,714 --> 00:29:17,756
Mau ke sana?

428
00:29:18,424 --> 00:29:20,885
Tidak. Aku tak suka tempat terpencil.

429
00:29:21,469 --> 00:29:24,805
Kita harus ke tempat
yang ramai dan berisik.

430
00:29:25,931 --> 00:29:26,807
Boleh.

431
00:29:35,232 --> 00:29:37,151
TERMINAL SHINSU

432
00:29:45,910 --> 00:29:46,952
Choi Se-jin!

433
00:29:52,208 --> 00:29:53,125
Apa ini?

434
00:29:54,126 --> 00:29:56,420
Kau datang mencariku?

435
00:29:57,046 --> 00:29:59,590
Apa maksudmu? Kau kabur karena aku?

436
00:30:01,675 --> 00:30:03,969
Aku selalu peringkat dua karena kau.

437
00:30:04,803 --> 00:30:08,265
Kecuali kau menghilang,
aku peringkat dua seumur hidup.

438
00:30:08,849 --> 00:30:11,894
Sayangnya, aku harus menjadi
peringkat satu.

439
00:30:12,978 --> 00:30:15,856
Jadi, aku akan pergi
ke tempat yang tak ada kau.

440
00:30:25,282 --> 00:30:27,159
KAU MENGINAP DI TEMPATKU MALAM INI?

441
00:30:27,243 --> 00:30:28,661
YA, AKU BERANGKAT SEKARANG

442
00:30:29,578 --> 00:30:30,496
"Jjun"?

443
00:30:31,163 --> 00:30:32,289
Siapa itu?

444
00:30:35,125 --> 00:30:37,670
Orang yang tetap menyayangiku
meski aku peringkat dua.

445
00:30:37,753 --> 00:30:38,587
Dia pria?

446
00:30:39,171 --> 00:30:40,172
Mungkin wanita?

447
00:30:42,174 --> 00:30:43,217
Mau naik, tidak?

448
00:30:43,300 --> 00:30:44,385
Ya.

449
00:30:45,553 --> 00:30:46,512
Hei.

450
00:30:47,221 --> 00:30:48,847
Jaga dirimu, Peringkat Satu.

451
00:30:49,515 --> 00:30:50,349
Selamat tinggal.

452
00:30:56,146 --> 00:30:58,857
LANGSUNG
SHINSU KE SEOUL

453
00:31:04,071 --> 00:31:05,489
Pak!

454
00:31:20,379 --> 00:31:22,047
{\an8}SUN JAE-GYU
MEMBUATKU BERSORAK

455
00:31:22,131 --> 00:31:24,133
{\an8}Apa ada artis bernama Sun Jae-gyu?

456
00:31:24,842 --> 00:31:27,928
Hei, ada tanda tangan
orang bernama Sun Jae-gyu…

457
00:31:28,012 --> 00:31:28,929
Itu aku.

458
00:31:30,222 --> 00:31:32,266
Kenapa kau selalu memajang namamu?

459
00:31:38,981 --> 00:31:40,566
Tak perlu lihat menu.

460
00:31:40,649 --> 00:31:42,484
Kita hanya harus pesan satu.

461
00:31:43,068 --> 00:31:43,986
Bulgogi cumi-babi.

462
00:31:47,823 --> 00:31:50,993
SUP AYAM HERBAL TERSEDIA

463
00:31:53,120 --> 00:31:54,538
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">-Ini enak.</font></i>
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">-Sungguh?</font></i>

464
00:31:55,039 --> 00:31:56,040
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Mau lagi?</font></i>

465
00:31:58,000 --> 00:31:59,627
Kau harus segera pulih.

466
00:32:00,878 --> 00:32:02,004
Buka mulutmu.

467
00:32:16,685 --> 00:32:18,062
Pesan dua bulgogi cumi-babi.

468
00:32:18,145 --> 00:32:19,355
Sup ayam herbal.

469
00:32:20,689 --> 00:32:22,107
Besar atau sedang?

470
00:32:22,191 --> 00:32:23,651
Sedang.

471
00:32:24,318 --> 00:32:25,944
Sialan.

472
00:32:26,528 --> 00:32:30,240
Aku akan membawamu ke pemandian
dan merebusmu di kolam paling panas.

473
00:32:30,324 --> 00:32:33,702
Sebelum kubuat pinggangmu
tampak seperti jam pasir,

474
00:32:33,786 --> 00:32:34,870
pesan yang besar.

475
00:32:34,953 --> 00:32:35,954
Mengerti?

476
00:32:36,955 --> 00:32:38,707
Jawab!

477
00:32:38,791 --> 00:32:39,708
Baik!

478
00:32:39,792 --> 00:32:41,669
Pesan yang besar.

479
00:32:41,752 --> 00:32:43,087
Yang besar.

480
00:32:48,258 --> 00:32:49,343
Dia masih sehat.

481
00:33:21,417 --> 00:33:22,793
Kau tak selera makan?

482
00:33:27,005 --> 00:33:27,840
Begini.

483
00:33:29,258 --> 00:33:33,679
Aku pernah kehilangan uang, teman,
bahkan semangat hidup.

484
00:33:34,221 --> 00:33:37,474
Satu hal yang tak pernah hilang
adalah selera makan.

485
00:33:38,976 --> 00:33:40,644
Berarti kau pemilih makanan.

486
00:33:43,564 --> 00:33:47,693
Aku tak pernah punya sampah makanan
kecuali kulit semangka.

487
00:33:48,444 --> 00:33:49,278
Begitu.

488
00:33:58,370 --> 00:33:59,872
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Cara makan apa itu?</font></i>

489
00:34:00,581 --> 00:34:02,332
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Kurasa pernah kulihat.</font></i>

490
00:34:08,005 --> 00:34:08,964
Ada apa?

491
00:34:10,466 --> 00:34:11,383
Bukan apa-apa.

492
00:34:11,967 --> 00:34:13,802
Belum lama, kurasa aku melihat

493
00:34:14,344 --> 00:34:16,722
orang yang mirip denganmu
di kantor polisi.

494
00:34:19,308 --> 00:34:20,184
Kau melihatnya?

495
00:34:22,770 --> 00:34:25,189
Aku di sana
karena melakukan sesuatu kepada wanita.

496
00:34:27,441 --> 00:34:29,318
Kau melakukan apa kepada wanita itu?

497
00:34:52,341 --> 00:34:53,425
-Apa?
-Ayo!

498
00:34:54,510 --> 00:34:55,844
Dasar berandal.

499
00:34:55,928 --> 00:34:58,222
Beraninya kau sentuh mobilku.

500
00:34:58,305 --> 00:34:59,515
Kau gila?

501
00:34:59,598 --> 00:35:01,642
Ini baru kubelikan kemarin.

502
00:35:01,725 --> 00:35:02,935
Aku tak menyentuh.

503
00:35:03,018 --> 00:35:05,103
Halo? Polisi?

504
00:35:05,687 --> 00:35:09,191
-Aku mau lapor.
-Suruh mereka tangkap orang gila ini.

505
00:35:09,274 --> 00:35:11,819
-Astaga!
-Mau lapor atau gugat, nanti saja.

506
00:35:11,902 --> 00:35:12,736
Minggir.

507
00:35:12,820 --> 00:35:14,655
Minggir sekarang juga.

508
00:35:18,992 --> 00:35:21,203
-Aku harus ambil foto.
-Ayolah.

509
00:35:22,496 --> 00:35:23,956
Lihat baik-baik.

510
00:35:24,039 --> 00:35:25,123
Minggir.

511
00:35:30,587 --> 00:35:32,673
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Aku hanya menyentuhnya sedikit.</font></i>

512
00:35:33,298 --> 00:35:34,633
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">"Menyentuhnya"?</font></i>

513
00:35:35,133 --> 00:35:36,760
Kebetulan ada suaminya.

514
00:35:36,844 --> 00:35:38,011
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Di depan suaminya?</font></i>

515
00:35:39,221 --> 00:35:42,224
Ini sering terjadi, bukan masalah.
Jangan khawatir.

516
00:35:46,019 --> 00:35:47,187
Mungkinkah…

517
00:35:49,189 --> 00:35:51,525
luka di tangan Pak Hong…

518
00:35:53,235 --> 00:35:54,319
Itu perbuatanmu?

519
00:36:06,957 --> 00:36:09,334
Kenapa ada guru di sini?

520
00:36:16,550 --> 00:36:18,760
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Mungkin itu alasan penghargaan Han-gyul</font></i>

521
00:36:18,844 --> 00:36:20,012
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">-batal.</font></i>
-Tanganku.

522
00:36:36,987 --> 00:36:38,572
Han-gyul terlambat.

523
00:36:38,655 --> 00:36:40,699
Kurasa hari ini sampai di sini saja.

524
00:36:46,330 --> 00:36:48,081
Pak Sun, wajahmu…

525
00:36:49,458 --> 00:36:50,375
Wajahmu agak…

526
00:37:05,307 --> 00:37:08,435
Astaga, seorang pria
tak boleh berwajah begini

527
00:37:08,518 --> 00:37:09,728
hanya karena makanan.

528
00:37:14,441 --> 00:37:16,777
Kenapa kau konyol sekali?

529
00:37:17,903 --> 00:37:21,531
Aku cepat pulih.
Ini akan hilang dalam satu jam.

530
00:37:23,075 --> 00:37:26,161
Jika kau punya alergi,
seharusnya aku makan sendirian.

531
00:37:27,454 --> 00:37:28,497
Ayolah.

532
00:37:29,247 --> 00:37:31,833
Jika begitu, kau tak menikmati.

533
00:37:31,917 --> 00:37:34,586
Makanan paling enak jika disantap bersama.

534
00:37:34,670 --> 00:37:35,671
Benar?

535
00:37:45,555 --> 00:37:46,390
Kau tertawa?

536
00:38:01,905 --> 00:38:02,990
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Jangan tersenyum.</font></i>

537
00:38:04,533 --> 00:38:05,784
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Jangan senang.</font></i>

538
00:38:07,035 --> 00:38:08,537
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Jangan bahagia.</font></i>

539
00:38:18,505 --> 00:38:19,548
Biar kulihat wajahmu.

540
00:39:17,314 --> 00:39:18,356
Astaga!

541
00:39:29,993 --> 00:39:31,870
Jangan pernah

542
00:39:32,662 --> 00:39:34,539
menyentuh tubuhku lagi. Paham?

543
00:39:55,519 --> 00:39:56,728
Ya, Han-gyul.

544
00:39:58,855 --> 00:39:59,773
Baiklah.

545
00:40:00,357 --> 00:40:01,483
Dengan siapa?

546
00:40:03,735 --> 00:40:04,653
Di mana?

547
00:40:05,779 --> 00:40:07,030
Ada apa?

548
00:40:08,782 --> 00:40:09,950
Kau punya uang?

549
00:40:11,910 --> 00:40:12,828
Aku mengerti.

550
00:40:13,495 --> 00:40:16,540
Setelah sampai,
belikan dia makan dan jaga dia.

551
00:40:17,124 --> 00:40:19,584
Nanti kabarkan lokasimu, akan kujemput.

552
00:40:21,336 --> 00:40:22,462
Sampai nanti.

553
00:40:24,005 --> 00:40:25,340
Kurasa aku harus pergi.

554
00:40:25,423 --> 00:40:27,342
Kenapa? Di mana Han-gyul?

555
00:40:27,425 --> 00:40:28,677
Dia bersama siapa?

556
00:40:31,763 --> 00:40:32,597
Itu…

557
00:40:33,473 --> 00:40:36,601
Teman sekelas bernama Choi Se-jin
kabur dari rumah.

558
00:40:36,685 --> 00:40:37,811
Dia mengikutinya.

559
00:40:37,894 --> 00:40:39,688
-Se-jin?
-Ya.

560
00:40:39,771 --> 00:40:41,731
Aku tak bisa mengantar. Hati-hati.

561
00:40:44,234 --> 00:40:45,610
"Hati-hati"?

562
00:40:46,695 --> 00:40:49,447
Aku wali kelas mereka, bukan kau, Pak Sun.

563
00:40:55,036 --> 00:40:56,121
Kita harus ke mana?

564
00:41:00,500 --> 00:41:01,334
Seoul.

565
00:41:10,135 --> 00:41:11,887
PERTEMUAN ORANG TUA DAN GURU

566
00:41:11,970 --> 00:41:13,305
Mohon jaga anakku.

567
00:41:13,388 --> 00:41:15,348
Tentu. Terima kasih sudah datang.

568
00:41:16,641 --> 00:41:18,101
Halo, Bu.

569
00:41:18,185 --> 00:41:19,686
Aku ayah A-ram.

570
00:41:20,729 --> 00:41:23,565
Terima kasih sudah meluangkan
waktu sibukmu.

571
00:41:24,232 --> 00:41:27,277
A-ram pasti senang
punya ayah yang perhatian.

572
00:41:27,360 --> 00:41:28,361
Benar.

573
00:41:29,696 --> 00:41:30,530
Terima kasih.

574
00:41:39,873 --> 00:41:41,875
AKUR DENGAN TEMAN DAN BERTANGGUNG JAWAB…

575
00:41:48,590 --> 00:41:49,424
AYAH OH A-RAM

576
00:41:49,507 --> 00:41:51,635
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Bagaimana harimu? Apa menyenangkan?</font></i>

577
00:41:53,845 --> 00:41:56,598
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Jika ada kesulitan di sekolah,</font></i>
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">beri tahu aku.</font></i>

578
00:41:56,681 --> 00:42:00,310
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Seperti katamu, aku cukup perhatian.</font></i>

579
00:42:00,393 --> 00:42:04,439
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Kau pakai parfum apa saat di sekolah?</font></i>
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Aku terus mengingat wanginya.</font></i>

580
00:42:06,107 --> 00:42:08,652
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Kenapa tak menjawab? Aku merindukanmu.</font></i>

581
00:42:10,612 --> 00:42:12,739
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Kau di mana? Bisa bertemu sebentar?</font></i>

582
00:42:22,916 --> 00:42:24,251
Aku sangat kecewa.

583
00:42:26,336 --> 00:42:27,420
Apakah benar?

584
00:42:27,504 --> 00:42:29,631
Mustahil. Bu Bom tak akan begitu.

585
00:42:29,714 --> 00:42:30,882
Ada buktinya.

586
00:42:30,966 --> 00:42:33,551
Jika tidak, kenapa ibu A-ram seperti itu?

587
00:42:33,635 --> 00:42:36,930
Dia berpura-pura punya etika,
tetapi menjadi selingkuhan.

588
00:42:37,013 --> 00:42:40,183
Dia menjijikkan, aku jadi mual.

589
00:42:47,649 --> 00:42:48,608
Ada apa?

590
00:42:54,239 --> 00:42:55,073
Bukan apa-apa.

591
00:42:58,285 --> 00:42:59,286
Mari pergi…

592
00:43:02,163 --> 00:43:03,206
ke Seoul.

593
00:43:36,906 --> 00:43:38,533
Hei, Han-gyul Jahat.

594
00:43:39,534 --> 00:43:40,493
"Han-gyul Jahat"?

595
00:43:40,577 --> 00:43:43,413
Ini sebabnya kau kupanggil Han-gyul Jahat.

596
00:43:43,496 --> 00:43:45,623
Aku kabur dari rumah karena kau.

597
00:43:46,207 --> 00:43:47,959
Aku ingin ke tempat kau tak ada.

598
00:43:48,043 --> 00:43:50,503
Kenapa kau ikut dan menggangguku?

599
00:43:51,212 --> 00:43:52,339
Kau tak lapar?

600
00:43:53,298 --> 00:43:54,883
Mau makan di Sungai Han?

601
00:43:56,843 --> 00:43:59,095
Buat apa anak kabur
berlaku romantis begitu?

602
00:43:59,971 --> 00:44:02,974
Aku tak kemari untuk melakukan
hal normal begitu.

603
00:44:03,767 --> 00:44:05,602
Ini kali pertama aku ke Seoul.

604
00:44:06,186 --> 00:44:07,020
Apa?

605
00:44:07,937 --> 00:44:10,273
Kau tak pernah ke Seoul World Tower?

606
00:44:10,357 --> 00:44:11,858
Pernah lihat di internet.

607
00:44:14,069 --> 00:44:17,447
Ini kali pertamaku.
Aku harus melakukan sesuatu.

608
00:44:18,156 --> 00:44:21,326
Kita tak makan siang karena naik bus.

609
00:44:24,412 --> 00:44:26,081
Kau boleh kabur dan lainnya

610
00:44:26,581 --> 00:44:28,249
setelah makan.

611
00:44:29,167 --> 00:44:30,335
Ayo.

612
00:44:32,253 --> 00:44:33,213
Ikuti aku.

613
00:44:44,808 --> 00:44:46,810
Bagaimana rasanya terlalu berbakat?

614
00:44:50,939 --> 00:44:53,817
Aku selalu kurang berbakat.

615
00:44:55,026 --> 00:44:57,487
Aku gagal masuk ke sekolah bagus,

616
00:44:57,570 --> 00:44:59,280
juga selalu peringkat dua.

617
00:45:00,949 --> 00:45:03,576
Kau peringkat satu meski tak mau kuliah.

618
00:45:04,285 --> 00:45:06,329
Kau selalu peringkat satu.

619
00:45:07,705 --> 00:45:08,748
Kau iri?

620
00:45:10,041 --> 00:45:11,334
Aku frustrasi.

621
00:45:13,503 --> 00:45:14,879
Boleh aku bertanya?

622
00:45:16,089 --> 00:45:17,966
Bagaimana rasanya punya orang tua?

623
00:45:19,092 --> 00:45:20,718
Sangat menyebalkan.

624
00:45:21,261 --> 00:45:23,555
Tak punya orang tua lebih menyebalkan.

625
00:45:25,014 --> 00:45:27,267
Aku tak bisa bersama ayahku sehari pun.

626
00:45:27,350 --> 00:45:29,644
Aku ingin bersama ayahku sehari saja.

627
00:45:29,727 --> 00:45:31,563
Aku tak cocok bicara dengan Ibu.

628
00:45:31,646 --> 00:45:33,690
Andai aku bisa bicara dengan ibuku.

629
00:45:34,732 --> 00:45:36,568
Pamanmu sangat baik.

630
00:45:37,360 --> 00:45:39,446
Sebaik apa pun, dia bukan ibuku.

631
00:45:41,156 --> 00:45:42,699
Kata Hong Jung-pyo,

632
00:45:43,408 --> 00:45:45,785
tak ada orang tua,
tak bisa dapat Bakti Orang Tua.

633
00:45:46,578 --> 00:45:49,831
Aku marah bukan karena
batal dapat penghargaan.

634
00:45:51,207 --> 00:45:53,084
Aku marah karena merasa dia benar.

635
00:45:55,211 --> 00:45:57,589
Kadang, berbakti kepada pamanku

636
00:45:57,672 --> 00:46:00,675
hanya terasa
seperti membayar kebaikannya untukku.

637
00:46:07,056 --> 00:46:07,891
Han-gyul Jahat.

638
00:46:09,434 --> 00:46:11,227
Kau ingin sekali menang dariku.

639
00:46:12,812 --> 00:46:14,022
Pada situasi ini,

640
00:46:14,522 --> 00:46:16,900
kau memainkan "aku tak punya orang tua".

641
00:46:16,983 --> 00:46:19,277
Kau membuatku tampak buruk.

642
00:46:30,205 --> 00:46:32,165
STASIUN SUNGAI HAN PUKUL 20.00

643
00:46:36,753 --> 00:46:39,756
Kuharap kau sudah membuat
kenangan indah di Seoul.

644
00:46:40,298 --> 00:46:41,674
Senang bicara denganmu.

645
00:46:43,092 --> 00:46:44,093
Kau mau ke mana?

646
00:46:45,762 --> 00:46:46,596
Se-jin!

647
00:46:47,514 --> 00:46:48,348
Hei!

648
00:46:55,188 --> 00:46:56,272
Kau sedang apa?

649
00:46:56,356 --> 00:46:59,567
Karena pot bodoh itu, pinggangku sakit.

650
00:47:00,944 --> 00:47:03,821
Ini gawat. Besok ulang tahun istriku.

651
00:47:03,905 --> 00:47:05,907
Pergelangan tanganku juga sakit

652
00:47:05,990 --> 00:47:09,327
dan leherku kaku. Keadaanku parah.

653
00:47:09,410 --> 00:47:11,246
Jika ini sepuluh tahun lalu,

654
00:47:11,329 --> 00:47:13,790
ketika Sun Jae-gyu datang ke kantor,

655
00:47:13,873 --> 00:47:16,876
aku akan mengunci kepala dan mencekiknya.

656
00:47:16,960 --> 00:47:17,919
Benar.

657
00:47:18,711 --> 00:47:19,921
Omong-omong,

658
00:47:20,588 --> 00:47:23,716
besok festival olahraga,
tetapi guru penjas tak sehat.

659
00:47:24,717 --> 00:47:26,177
Kau dengar Kepala Sekolah.

660
00:47:26,261 --> 00:47:29,180
Festival olahraga sekolah kita
seperti olimpiade Shinsu.

661
00:47:29,264 --> 00:47:30,682
Dia sangat serius.

662
00:47:31,766 --> 00:47:33,017
Omong-omong,

663
00:47:33,101 --> 00:47:35,770
bagaimana kalau kita olahraga bersama?

664
00:47:36,354 --> 00:47:37,313
-Olahraga?
-Ya.

665
00:47:37,397 --> 00:47:38,982
Aku ikut.

666
00:47:39,065 --> 00:47:41,109
Olahraga apa yang bagus?

667
00:47:41,192 --> 00:47:43,695
Jika ingin cepat punya keterampilan,

668
00:47:43,778 --> 00:47:45,947
-kita harus tinju.
-Tinju.

669
00:47:46,030 --> 00:47:48,157
Cepat? Lututku akan sakit.

670
00:47:48,241 --> 00:47:51,619
Kalau begitu yang ringan,
seperti sepak bola?

671
00:47:52,203 --> 00:47:55,415
Kepribadianku introver,
tak bisa main dengan orang asing.

672
00:47:55,498 --> 00:47:56,874
Lantas mendaki?

673
00:47:56,958 --> 00:47:58,585
Itu paling bagus untuk otot.

674
00:47:58,668 --> 00:48:00,837
Kau tak tahu aku takut ketinggian?

675
00:48:00,920 --> 00:48:03,089
Kau tolak semua! Lantas kau mau apa?

676
00:48:03,172 --> 00:48:04,257
Entahlah.

677
00:48:06,342 --> 00:48:07,302
Aku tahu.

678
00:48:07,969 --> 00:48:11,306
Lutut tak akan sakit,
bisa dilakukan introver,

679
00:48:11,389 --> 00:48:13,850
juga yang takut ketinggian. Ini sempurna.

680
00:48:15,059 --> 00:48:15,935
Apa itu?

681
00:48:17,854 --> 00:48:19,355
{\an8}TIM TERBAIK MURYONG

682
00:48:19,439 --> 00:48:20,648
JUJITSU

683
00:48:37,415 --> 00:48:39,876
Pak Hong tak datang sesuai janji.

684
00:48:39,959 --> 00:48:41,252
Kenapa kau datang?

685
00:48:41,878 --> 00:48:44,213
Aku ingin seperti paman Han-gyul.

686
00:48:44,297 --> 00:48:45,131
Apa?

687
00:48:46,799 --> 00:48:48,301
Dengar, Bu.

688
00:48:48,384 --> 00:48:51,929
Setelah usia 80 tahun,
gigi tak bisa tumbuh lagi.

689
00:48:52,013 --> 00:48:55,642
Siput bisa melintasi lautan
dan kacang rebus bisa bertunas,

690
00:48:56,142 --> 00:48:59,854
tetapi jika pria tak bisa seperti dia,
apalagi wanita?

691
00:48:59,937 --> 00:49:02,065
Karena itu aku kemari!

692
00:49:02,148 --> 00:49:05,526
Karena guru pria
meremehkan wanita seperti ini,

693
00:49:05,610 --> 00:49:08,404
jelas siswa lelaki
tak mematuhi guru wanita!

694
00:49:08,488 --> 00:49:10,698
Konon wibawa guru jatuh ke lantai.

695
00:49:10,782 --> 00:49:13,117
Namun, wibawa guru wanita?

696
00:49:13,201 --> 00:49:15,078
Ada di bawah tanah!

697
00:49:17,830 --> 00:49:18,998
-Halo.
-Halo.

698
00:49:19,874 --> 00:49:20,708
Halo.

699
00:49:25,380 --> 00:49:26,589
Bagus kalian datang.

700
00:49:26,673 --> 00:49:27,507
Guru.

701
00:49:28,132 --> 00:49:31,469
Aku ingin cepat pandai.

702
00:49:31,552 --> 00:49:32,804
Butuh berapa lama?

703
00:49:32,887 --> 00:49:35,765
Itu tergantung masing-masing orang,

704
00:49:35,848 --> 00:49:38,810
tetapi kujamin murid di dojoku belajar

705
00:49:38,893 --> 00:49:41,187
dua kali lebih cepat
daripada di dojo lain.

706
00:49:42,397 --> 00:49:45,483
Kau pasti punya semacam metode rahasia.

707
00:49:48,027 --> 00:49:51,864
Ada pemegang sabuk hitam legendaris
di dojo ini.

708
00:50:02,250 --> 00:50:05,545
Dia salah satu
dari 700 ahli jujitsu di Korea.

709
00:50:14,762 --> 00:50:18,015
Dia elite yang mendapat sabuk hitam
hanya dalam tujuh tahun.

710
00:50:22,103 --> 00:50:25,606
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Dia bahkan menguasai Putaran Imanari</font></i>
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">yang legendaris dengan sempurna.</font></i>

711
00:50:25,690 --> 00:50:27,150
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Dia kebanggaan dojo ini.</font></i>

712
00:50:29,569 --> 00:50:32,572
Jika berlatih dengannya,
kemampuan dan stamina kalian…

713
00:50:33,364 --> 00:50:34,574
akan cepat membaik.

714
00:50:36,492 --> 00:50:38,327
Kapan orang hebat itu datang?

715
00:50:39,412 --> 00:50:42,206
Dia biasanya datang di waktu ini.

716
00:50:42,957 --> 00:50:46,169
Entah apa yang terjadi.
Dia terlambat hari ini.

717
00:51:01,726 --> 00:51:02,977
Kau yakin dia di sini?

718
00:51:04,228 --> 00:51:06,397
Dia mengirim pesan lima menit lalu.

719
00:51:07,982 --> 00:51:10,234
Mungkin dia tak bisa menjawab
karena ada Se-jin.

720
00:51:13,279 --> 00:51:16,073
Mari berpencar. Aku ke kiri, kau ke kanan.

721
00:51:16,699 --> 00:51:17,575
Baiklah.

722
00:51:18,993 --> 00:51:20,703
Di mana bocah itu? Sial.

723
00:51:49,065 --> 00:51:49,899
Jjun!

724
00:51:52,276 --> 00:51:53,903
Aku merindukanmu!

725
00:51:54,529 --> 00:51:57,740
Aku tersesat. Seoul terlalu jauh.

726
00:51:57,824 --> 00:52:00,618
Aku lapar sekali.
Belikan aku makanan enak.

727
00:52:07,500 --> 00:52:09,168
-Paman!
-Hei.

728
00:52:10,753 --> 00:52:11,879
Kenapa sendirian?

729
00:52:12,380 --> 00:52:13,840
Di mana Choi Se-jin?

730
00:52:14,549 --> 00:52:16,425
-Dia hilang.
-Hilang?

731
00:52:17,760 --> 00:52:20,847
Aku tak beri tahu
karena Paman pasti cemas.

732
00:52:20,930 --> 00:52:22,849
Dia berkirim pesan dengan pria.

733
00:52:23,724 --> 00:52:25,852
Pria itu menyuruhnya…

734
00:52:27,687 --> 00:52:29,146
menginap di rumahnya.

735
00:52:29,856 --> 00:52:31,107
Di rumahnya?

736
00:52:32,024 --> 00:52:36,737
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Kereta Jalur Lingkar Dalam</font></i>
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">menuju Hangang Naru akan segera tiba.</font></i>

737
00:52:37,363 --> 00:52:40,908
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Kereta menuju Hangang Naru</font></i>
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">akan segera tiba.</font></i>

738
00:52:41,826 --> 00:52:43,536
Se-jin!

739
00:52:46,163 --> 00:52:46,998
Sial.

740
00:52:55,131 --> 00:52:55,965
Halo?

741
00:52:57,049 --> 00:52:57,884
Sudah ketemu.

742
00:52:58,926 --> 00:53:01,512
Kami baru naik kereta,
tetapi dia bersama seorang pria.

743
00:53:02,096 --> 00:53:03,139
Aku ke sana.

744
00:53:04,265 --> 00:53:07,268
Kita tak tahu itu siapa.
Entah dia akan berbuat apa.

745
00:53:07,351 --> 00:53:08,352
Kau harus tunggu aku.

746
00:53:11,147 --> 00:53:12,857
Tidak bisa, kereta akan berangkat.

747
00:53:12,940 --> 00:53:14,942
Kita bertemu di stasiun berikutnya.

748
00:53:15,026 --> 00:53:16,152
Stasiun berikut?

749
00:53:16,986 --> 00:53:18,070
Bagaimana…

750
00:53:18,779 --> 00:53:19,906
Halo? Halo…

751
00:53:19,989 --> 00:53:21,157
Naik kereta berikut.

752
00:53:24,493 --> 00:53:25,328
Jangan-jangan…

753
00:54:03,658 --> 00:54:05,201
{\an8}KECEPATAN ANDA SAAT INI

754
00:54:10,122 --> 00:54:12,208
{\an8}PELAN-PELAN

755
00:55:03,175 --> 00:55:05,928
STASIUN INI: HANGANG NARU

756
00:55:10,933 --> 00:55:12,309
-Semangat!
-Semangat!

757
00:55:14,020 --> 00:55:14,979
Semangat!

758
00:55:18,482 --> 00:55:20,192
-Semangat!
-Apa ini?

759
00:55:23,863 --> 00:55:24,822
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Aku ke sana.</font></i>

760
00:55:25,531 --> 00:55:26,824
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Kau harus tunggu aku.</font></i>

761
00:55:29,618 --> 00:55:33,789
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Perhentian berikutnya,</font></i>
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Stasiun Hangang Naru.</font></i>

762
00:55:33,873 --> 00:55:34,874
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Pintu…</font></i>

763
00:55:37,418 --> 00:55:39,378
LINDUNGI BUMI!
TANPA BUMI, TAK ADA KITA

764
00:56:18,918 --> 00:56:19,835
Sudah kuduga.

765
00:56:27,551 --> 00:56:28,594
Apa?

766
00:56:30,387 --> 00:56:31,222
Choi Se-jin!

767
00:56:31,931 --> 00:56:34,642
Maaf, permisi. Mau lewat.

768
00:56:35,976 --> 00:56:37,394
Minggir!

769
00:56:39,522 --> 00:56:40,689
Minggir!

770
00:56:44,527 --> 00:56:45,820
Pak Sun?

771
00:57:40,958 --> 00:57:43,127
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Kini aku ingat</font></i>

772
00:57:43,961 --> 00:57:44,879
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">pria ini.</font></i>

773
00:58:57,493 --> 00:58:58,661
{\an8}Pak.

774
00:58:58,744 --> 00:59:00,621
{\an8}<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Sun Jae-gyu?</font></i>

775
00:59:00,704 --> 00:59:04,333
{\an8}<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Tadinya ingin kumaafkan,</font></i>
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">tetapi kini aku ingin balas dendam.</font></i>

776
00:59:04,416 --> 00:59:05,960
{\an8}Kau kehilangan separuh?

777
00:59:08,629 --> 00:59:09,505
{\an8}Bisa kau obati?

778
00:59:09,588 --> 00:59:11,215
{\an8}Kau sudah jatuh cinta padanya.

779
00:59:11,298 --> 00:59:14,843
{\an8}<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Apa yang dilakukan pria seperti</font></i>
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Sun Jae-gyu dengan wanita seperti itu?</font></i>

780
00:59:14,927 --> 00:59:17,429
{\an8}<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Wanita itu menangis sesenggukan.</font></i>

781
00:59:18,097 --> 00:59:19,890
{\an8}<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Mulai kini, perhatikan baik-baik.</font></i>

782
00:59:20,432 --> 00:59:22,184
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Itu jelas lampu hijau.</font></i>

783
00:59:22,268 --> 00:59:23,310
<i><font face="sansSerif" color="white">Jae-gyu!</font></i>

